  <brief_title>Foveal Cone Outer Segment Resumption to Predict Visual Recovery After Macular Hole Surgery</brief_title>
  <official_title>Foveal Cone Outer Segment Resumption to Predict Visual Recovery After Macular Hole Surgery</official_title>
